{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-detail-page-js","path":"/time-off-sick","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Buckinghamshire HR service desk","basePath":"https://bucks-temp-name.com","gaConfig":{"id":"UA-129132977-3"}}},"contentfulPage":{"title":"Time off sick","metaTitle":"Taking time off sick ","metaDescription":"This section explains what happens with work and illness – what to do if you’re ill or have a doctor’s appointment, what happens with your pay when you’re off sick, long term illness and frequent illness.","parentPage":null,"intro":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>On the first day you’re ill, phone your manager as soon as possible.</li>\n<li>When you get back to work, fill in a form with details of your illness: <a href=\"https://assets.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/3h1U9c0QLTg8UCnFd1Uoc/c2cddb2bb1dcbad18ed0cea8fea2196d/self-certification-form.docx\">Self certification form (Word doc, 21k)</a></li>\n<li>If you’re off work for more than seven days you’ll need a medical certificate.</li>\n</ul>"}},"body":null,"hero":{"headline":"Time off sick hero","subHeading":"TIme off sick subheading","image":[{"title":"Time off sick","description":"","file":{"details":{"size":131641,"image":{"width":1611,"height":484}},"fileName":"sickness--large.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg","url":"//images.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/IXHucSRmG8nFQ4dPQ8lSr/5fcb571edc4db77f8baa83d3409cd8c9/sickness--large.jpg"}}]},"collapsibleLinks":[{"title":"What happens when you’re ill?","ariaLabel":"A more expressive What happens when you are ill statement","content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Stay in touch with your manager, so they know how you’re doing and if your illness is lasting longer than expected. Your manager will record your absence on our admin\nsystem, SAP.</p>\n<p>When you get back to work, catch up with your manager. They will tell you anything\nyou’ve missed, and you can explain about your illness and any underlying factors. They will then fill in a return to work discussion form. </p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"//assets.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/1umU4bfX0NursCM5hdGlrh/74be1e9a76785ec41808fb81e004d8da/Return_to_Work_Short_Term_Absence.rtf\" title=\"Return to Work Form for up to 7 Days Off\">Return to Work Form: Up to 7 Days Off</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"//assets.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/2KFgm51C7UYvGCmxhAW2d8/1b7faf9aa074c5ed22f0e55e5ec0a69b/Return_to_Work_Longer_Term_Absence.rtf\" title=\"Return to Work Form for more than 7 Days Off\">Return to Work Form: More than 7 Days Off</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"open":false,"link":null,"mediaLink":null},{"title":"Going to a medical appointment","ariaLabel":null,"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Try and arrange doctor and dentist appointments outside work hours, but if not\nthen try to be off work for no more than an hour. If you need to take longer, talk to your manager first and they may agree extra time if you need it.</p>"}},"open":false,"link":null,"mediaLink":null},{"title":"Pay when you’re ill","ariaLabel":null,"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>To start with you’ll be paid as normal when you’re off ill. How long you’ll continue to be paid depends on how long you’ve worked at the council.</p>"}},"open":false,"link":{"id":"e4c5a43d-fcad-5d71-9189-846066f7883c","title":"Sick pay scheme","slug":"sick-pay-scheme"},"mediaLink":null},{"title":"Long term illness","ariaLabel":"Long term illness Long term illness","content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>If you’re ill for longer than 28 days, it’s considered long term illness. We’ll need to find out more about your illness and then see how we can help you back to work.</p>"}},"open":false,"link":{"id":"7d31c1d3-4eff-576d-bc56-67655c0d2072","title":"Long term illness","slug":"long-term-illness"},"mediaLink":null},{"title":"Frequent illness","ariaLabel":"Read more about taking time off sick frequently","content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Everyone gets ill from time to time, but if it happens too often it can become a problem.</p>\n<p>All days off sick are recorded so we can pick up on this.\nYou’ll need to meet your manager to discuss your illness if:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You’re off ill more than three times in a 6-month period</li>\n<li>Your time off ill has a noticeable pattern, for example if it always happens around weekends or special occasions.</li>\n</ul>"}},"open":false,"link":{"id":"fca748c6-63b8-53ec-bd99-05982b0d7762","title":"Frequent illness","slug":"frequent-illness"},"mediaLink":null},{"title":"Illness policy","ariaLabel":"Illness policy containing links to documents","content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Full details on time off sick are in our <a href=\"//assets.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/6Ramm6Mt2ISpE8pahajgAB/ff98bf0eaecbef2895de7941a92e54ac/BC_Health_and_Attendance_Policy_v1.4_Mar_2020.doc\" title=\"Health and Attendance Policy\">Health and Attendance Policy</a>. Additional information can be found in our <a href=\"//assets.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/4eTNruKG1QcKB3dDwmv85Y/ed33fc9f76e95d9ae43ceec6792e8be4/BC_Health_and_Attendance_Guidance_Sep_2020.rtf\">Health and Attendance Guidance</a>.</p>"}},"open":null,"link":null,"mediaLink":null}],"mediaLink":[{"id":"ba9b3500-26cf-57ef-9166-4bbfdb44746a","type":"doc","title":"Self certification form ","mediaLink":null,"description":"(Word doc, 21k)","mediaFile":{"file":{"fileName":"self-certification-form.docx","url":"//assets.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/3h1U9c0QLTg8UCnFd1Uoc/c2cddb2bb1dcbad18ed0cea8fea2196d/self-certification-form.docx"}}},{"id":"4e4fe460-8655-5fad-83d5-c4fde23d292f","type":"doc","title":"Health and Attendance Policy","mediaLink":null,"description":"(Word doc, 38k)","mediaFile":{"file":{"fileName":"BC Health and Attendance Policy v1.4 Mar 2020.doc","url":"//assets.ctfassets.net/fxzi1pcakms5/2P0K2QC0JkePmzKveASiUk/48114e17e065c543e47c0a1279d8c69c/BC_Health_and_Attendance_Policy_v1.4_Mar_2020.doc"}}},{"id":"c333ddde-c8e1-5425-b035-31636ad7fee1","type":"doc","title":"Health an